<script>
import axios from "axios";
export default {
  name: 'App',
  methods: {
    async post(){
      const response = await axios({
        method: "post",
        url:"https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts",
        data:{
          title:"My first blog",
          body:"visit on www.Google.com",
          userID:"1"
        }
      });
      console.log(response.data);
    }
  }
}
</script>

<template>
  <button @click="post" class="btn btn-primary">Post</button>

</template>
